step.tex:
y = 500e^{7x} + 600e^{-7x}\\
\text{Differentiating the above equation we get }\\ \begin{align} \dfrac{dy}{dx} &= \dfrac{d \left(500e^{7x} + 600e^{-7x}\right)}{dx}\\ &= 3500e^{7x} - 4200e^{-7x}\\ \end{align}\\
\text{Further differentiating }\dfrac{dy}{dx} \text{ we get}\\ \begin{align} \dfrac{d^2 y}{dx^2} &= \dfrac{d \left( 3500e^{7x} - 4200e^{-7x}\right)}{dx}\\ &=7* 3500e^{7x} - (-7)*4200e^{-7x}\\ &= 24500e^{7x} + 29400e^{-7x}\\ \end{align}
